p.d: The Outdoor Sports Show showcases a diverse array of outdoor sports and returns to screens in 2020 to take millions of viewers around the world on a globe-trotting journey to take in a range of world class races, as well as introduce the characters and athletes competing. There are no limits to the content of The Outdoor Sports Show, which will cover professional and recreational to extreme and adventure sports.
